title: 594. 10 Takeaways from Week 4
itunes:title: 594. 10 Takeaways from Week 4
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and pick ten storylines that stood out from Week 4 of the NFL season. To start off, the guys discuss how Bills QB Josh Allen is playing so well (1:07). Next, the trio examine the Browns running all over the Cowboys in a big win (5:21). Later, the guys look at Bucs QB Tom Brady and Chargers QB Justin Herbert's impressive performances (14:25). To wrap up the show, DJ, Bucky and Rhett touch on the Colts' defense being so dominate against the Bears (35:31). All that and more in this packed episode.
